// Flagship article-page full conversion (proof of P2 pattern).
// Source: docs/articles/why-programming-for-the-browser-needs-a-different-kind-of-language-devto-2026-04-27.md
// 84 source lines → ~165 scrml lines. Body preserved verbatim except for:
//   - Frontmatter dropped (scrml file, not markdown)
//   - Headers wrapped in <h1>/<h2>/<h3> with Tailwind utility classes
